== English ==

=== Noun phrase ===

# A place where a homeless person will often get a roof over his/her head; a temporary address which provides sleep-in facilities for displaced persons
# A school or other sturdy public building used as temporary housing during a period of danger, due to a severe weather problem like a hurricane, or other crisis, for a mass of displaced or threatened population
#Any of the above, but for domestic animals

